<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="sr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Kelt PUB Beer List</title>

<style>

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
}

body{
font-family:Georgia,serif;
background:
linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,.82),rgba(0,0,0,.94)),
url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1510812431401-41d2bd2722f3?q=80&w=1800&auto=format&fit=crop');
background-size:cover;
background-position:center;
background-attachment:fixed;
color:#f5e6c8;
min-height:100vh;
padding:18px;
}

.container{
max-width:950px;
margin:auto;
}

.header{
text-align:center;
padding:35px 10px;
}

.header h1{
font-size:62px;
letter-spacing:5px;
color:#f1d79a;
text-shadow:0 0 18px rgba(0,0,0,.6);
}

.header p{
margin-top:10px;
color:#b9d8b9;
letter-spacing:4px;
font-size:14px;
}

.section-title{
margin:45px 0 22px;
font-size:36px;
text-align:center;
color:#d8b66c;
text-shadow:0 0 12px rgba(0,0,0,.4);
padding-bottom:10px;
border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,215,120,.2);
}

.grid{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:1fr;
gap:18px;
}

.card{
background:rgba(20,28,20,.82);
backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
border:1px solid rgba(255,215,120,.15);
border-radius:24px;
padding:22px;
box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.4);
transition:.25s;
}

.card:hover{
transform:translateY(-4px);
border-color:rgba(255,215,120,.4);
}

.top{
display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
align-items:center;
gap:10px;
margin-bottom:8px;
}

.top h3{
font-size:28px;
color:#fff2d2;
}

.price{
font-size:21px;
font-weight:bold;
color:#e0bb68;
}

.style{
margin-top:6px;
color:#d4b06d;
font-size:14px;
letter-spacing:1px;
}

.desc{
margin-top:12px;
color:#ddd0b3;
line-height:1.6;
font-size:15px;
}

.eng{
margin-top:10px;
font-size:14px;
color:#b8c7b8;
font-style:italic;
line-height:1.5;
}

.footer{
text-align:center;
margin-top:50px;
padding-bottom:30px;
color:#b9d8b9;
letter-spacing:3px;
font-size:13px;
}

@media(max-width:700px){

.top{
flex-direction:column;
align-items:flex-start;
}

.top h3{
font-size:24px;
}

.price{
font-size:20px;
}

}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

<div class="header">
<h1>KELT PUB</h1>
<p>BEER LIST</p>
</div>

<h2 class="section-title">🍺 TOČENO PIVO / DRAFT BEER</h2>

<div class="grid">

<div class="card">
<div class="top">
<h3>Madri Excepcional</h3>
<div class="price">3.00 KM</div>
</div>
<div class="style">Spanish Style Lager • Španija / Spain</div>
<div class="desc">
Lagano premium lager pivo zlatne boje sa blagom gorčinom i veoma osvježavajućim završetkom.
</div>
<div class="eng">
Light premium lager with smooth bitterness and refreshing finish.
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<div class="top">
<h3>Stella Artois</h3>
<div class="price">2.40 KM</div>
</div>
<div class="style">Belgian Premium Lager • Belgija / Belgium</div>
<div class="desc">
Klasični evropski lager elegantnog ukusa i fine arome hmelja.
</div>
<div class="eng">
Classic European lager with elegant taste and fine hop aroma.
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<div class="top">
<h3>Nikšićko Tamno</h3>
<div class="price">2.40 KM</div>
</div>
<div class="style">Dark Lager • Crna Gora / Montenegro</div>
<div class="desc">
Tamni lager bogatog ukusa sa notama karamele i prženog slada.
</div>
<div class="eng">
Dark lager with caramel notes and roasted malt aroma.
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<div class="top">
<h3>Jelen</h3>
<div class="price">2.40 KM</div>
</div>
<div class="style">Pale Lager • Srbija / Serbia</div>
<div class="desc">
Lagano i veoma pitko domaće lager pivo osvježavajućeg karaktera.
</div>
<div class="eng">
Smooth and refreshing domestic pale lager.
</div>
</div>

</div>

<h2 class="section-title">🍾 PIVO U FLAŠICI / BOTTLED BEER</h2>

<div class="grid">

<div class="card">
<div class="top">
<h3>Nikšićko • 0.33l</h3>
<div class="price">2.50 KM</div>
</div>
<div class="style">Montenegro Lager • Crna Gora / Montenegro</div>
<div class="desc">
Tradicionalni lager punog ukusa i prijatne gorčine.
</div>
<div class="eng">
Traditional lager with rich flavor and balanced bitterness.
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<div class="top">
<h3>Jelen • 0.33l</h3>
<div class="price">2.40 KM</div>
</div>
<div class="style">Serbian Lager • Srbija / Serbia</div>
<div class="desc">
Pitko domaće lager pivo osvježavajućeg karaktera.
</div>
<div class="eng">
Easy-drinking lager with refreshing taste.
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<div class="top">
<h3>Bavaria • 0.25l</h3>
<div class="price">3.50 KM</div>
</div>
<div class="style">Dutch Lager • Holandija / Netherlands</div>
<div class="desc">
Holandski premium lager čistog i laganog ukusa.
</div>
<div class="eng">
Dutch premium lager with clean and crisp taste.
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<div class="top">
<h3>Stella Artois • 0.33l</h3>
<div class="price">3.50 KM</div>
</div>
<div class="style">Belgian Premium Lager • Belgija / Belgium</div>
<div class="desc">
Elegantni lager sa blagom aromom hmelja.
</div>
<div class="eng">
Elegant lager with smooth hop aroma.
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<div class="top">
<h3>Staropramen • 0.33l</h3>
<div class="price">3.00 KM</div>
</div>
<div class="style">Czech Lager • Češka / Czech Republic</div>
<div class="desc">
Češki lager bogatijeg pivskog karaktera.
</div>
<div class="eng">
Traditional Czech lager with fuller body.
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<div class="top">
<h3>Beck's • 0.33l</h3>
<div class="price">3.00 KM</div>
</div>
<div class="style">German Pilsner • Njemačka / Germany</div>
<div class="desc">
Njemački pilsner sa izraženijom gorčinom.
</div>
<div class="eng">
German pilsner with pronounced bitterness.
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<div class="top">
<h3>Blue Moon • 0.33l</h3>
<div class="price">4.00 KM</div>
</div>
<div class="style">Belgian White Ale • SAD / USA</div>
<div class="desc">
Pšenično pivo sa citrusnim i začinskim notama.
</div>
<div class="eng">
Wheat beer with citrus and spice notes.
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<div class="top">
<h3>Madri Excepcional • 0.33l</h3>
<div class="price">3.50 KM</div>
</div>
<div class="style">Spanish Style Lager • Španija / Spain</div>
<div class="desc">
Moderan lager laganog i čistog ukusa.
</div>
<div class="eng">
Modern lager with clean and refreshing taste.
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<div class="top">
<h3>Franziskaner • 0.50l</h3>
<div class="price">6.00 KM</div>
</div>
<div class="style">German Wheat Beer • Njemačka / Germany</div>
<div class="desc">
Bogato pšenično pivo sa voćnim i kremastim karakterom.
</div>
<div class="eng">
Rich wheat beer with fruity and creamy character.
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<div class="top">
<h3>Corona Extra • 0.33l</h3>
<div class="price">5.00 KM</div>
</div>
<div class="style">Mexican Lager • Meksiko / Mexico</div>
<div class="desc">
Lagano meksičko lager pivo idealno uz limetu.
</div>
<div class="eng">
Light Mexican lager best served with lime.
</div>
</div>

</div>

<div class="footer">
GOOD BEER • GOOD PEOPLE • GOOD TIMES
</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>